<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <!-- displays site properly based on user's device -->

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="./images/favicon-32x32.png">

    <title>Frontend Mentor | Four card feature section</title>

    <!-- Feel free to remove these styles or customise in your own stylesheet 👍 -->
    <style>
        

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            width: 1440px;
        }
        .row {
            background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 98%);
            padding:10px;
           
        }
        .ust{
            width:100%;
           
        }
        .sol{
            float:left;
            width:33%;
        }
        .orta {
            float:left;
            width: 33%;
        }
        .sag {
            float: left;
            width: 33%;
        }
        .card1 {
            background-color: white;
            margin-top: 250px;
            margin-right: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000;
            border-radius:7px;
           
        }
        .card2 {
            background-color: white;
            margin-top: 100px;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 4px #000;
            border-radius: 7px;
            margin-left:20px;
        }
        .card3 {
            background-color: white;
            margin-top: 50px;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 4px #000;
            border-radius: 7px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        .card4 {
            background-color: white;
            margin-top: 250px;
            margin-left: 40px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000;
            border-radius: 7px;
        }
        @@media only screen and (max-width:376px) {
            .row {
                width:375px;
                padding: 10px;
            }
         .ust{
             width:100%;
             margin-left:50px;
         }
            .sol {
                width:110%;
                margin-left:50px;
                margin-top:-220px;
            }
            .orta {
                width: 110%;
                margin-left: 25px;
                margin-top: -70px;
            }
            .sag {
                width: 115%;
                margin-left:7px;
                margin-top: -200px;
            }


        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="ust">
            <h2 style="text-align:center;">Reliable,efficent delivery</h2>
            <h2 style="text-align:center;"><strong>Powered by Technology</strong></h2>
            <p style="text-align:center;">
                Our Artificial Intelligence powered tools use millions of project data<br />points
                to ensure that your project is successful
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sol">
            <div class="card1">
                <div style="background-color:hsl(180, 62%, 55%);border-radius:7px;">
                    <p style="background-color: hsl(180, 62%, 55%);color:hsl(180, 62%, 55%);border-radius:7px;">KUBRA</p>
                </div>
                <h3 style="padding-top:20px;padding-left:20px;"><strong>Supervisor</strong></h3>
                <p style="padding-left:20px;color:hsl(229, 6%, 66%);">Monitors activity to identify project <br /> roadblocks</p>
                <img style="padding-left:230px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-right:50px;" src="~/img/icon-supervisor.svg" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="orta">
            <div class="card2">
                <div style="background-color:hsl(0, 78%, 62%);border-radius:7px;">
                    <p style="background-color:hsl(0, 78%, 62%);color:hsl(0, 78%, 62%);border-radius:7px;">KUBRA</p>
                </div>
                <h3 style="padding-top:20px;padding-left:20px;"><strong>Team Builder</strong></h3>
                <p style="padding-left:20px;color:hsl(229, 6%, 66%);">Scans our talent network to create the <br /> optimal team for your project</p>
                <img style="padding-left:230px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-right:50px;" src="~/img/icon-team-builder.svg" />
            </div>
            <div class="card3">
                <div style="background-color: hsl(34, 97%, 64%);border-radius:7px;">
                    <p style="background-color: hsl(34, 97%, 64%);color: hsl(34, 97%, 64%);border-radius:7px;">KUBRA</p>
                </div>
                <h3 style="padding-top:10px;padding-left:20px;"><strong>Karma</strong></h3>
                <p style="padding-left:20px;color:hsl(229, 6%, 66%);">Regularly evaluates our talent to ensure <br /> quality</p>
                <img style="padding-left:230px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-right:50px;" src="~/img/icon-karma.svg" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sag">
            <div class="card4">
                <div style="background-color:hsl(212, 86%, 64%);border-radius:7px;">
                    <p style="background-color:hsl(212, 86%, 64%);color:hsl(212, 86%, 64%);border-radius:7px;">KUBRA</p>
                </div>
                <h3 style="padding-top:20px;padding-left:20px;"><strong>Calculator</strong></h3>
                <p style="padding-left:20px;color:hsl(229, 6%, 66%);">Uses data from past projects to provide <br /> better delivery estimates</p>
                <img style="padding-left:220px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-right:50px;" src="~/img/icon-calculator.svg" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>


    



</body>
</html>